gtr 250\%\) The program first computes the (implied) Annualized Volatility from the daily returns (price_pctchange) for each stock, using \(	ext{Annualized Volatility}=\Delta(	ext{Daily Price})\cdot \sqrt{252}\), assuming 252 trading days every year. Any stock with an implied annual volatility of more than 250% will be removed from the selection (process). Implied volatility (annual_volatility) greater than 250% indicates extreme volatile price movements at some point during the last year. To actively manage potential short-term and long-term (portfolio) risks, and utilizing an equilibrium investment strategy; with the potential volatile stocks are exhibited, they will be eliminated in advance for that purpose. 程序首先从每只股票的日收益率（price_pctchange）计算（隐含的）年化波动率，使用公式 \(	ext{Annualized Volatility} = \Delta(	ext{Daily Price}) \cdot \sqrt{252}\)，假设每年有252个交易日。任何隐含年化波动率超过250%的股票将从选择（过程）中被移除。 隐含波动率（annual_volatility）大于250%表明在过去一年的某个时点存在极端波动的价格运动。为了积极管理潜在的短期和长期（投资组合）风险，并使用一个均衡的投资策略；展示潜在波动的股票将被提前淘汰。 Table 2.7: Implied Annualized Volatility Date Adj Close Symbol Annual Volatility % 2024-04-09 A 147.4000 32.3071 2024-04-09 AAL 13.9500 5.7103 2024-04-09 AAPL 169.6700 11.4971 2024-04-09 ABBV 168.5658 3.1786 2024-04-09 ABNB 162.6600 23.6726 2024-04-09 ABT 111.8851 27.5779 2024-04-09 ACGL 91.2200 -55.9092 2024-04-09 ACN 333.1600 12.6787 2024-04-09 ADBE 492.5500 27.1087 2024-04-09 ADI 204.1200 59.9662 Note: Output 2.2.4.a: First 10 rows are shown. Table: 2.2.4-a: Interactive Annual Volatility % (Volatility) table Table 2.8: Stocks Removed by Implied Volatility Symbol AAL ALGN APA APTV BBWI BIIB CCL CZR DRI DVN DXCM ENPH EOG EPAM EQT FANG FCX FICO FRT GEN HAL HES HST KIM MGM MRO NCLH NFLX NRG OKE OXY PARA PAYC PCG PXD RCL REG SMCI TPR TRGP UAL UBER ULTA VLO Note: Output 2.2.4.b: Last 10 rows are shown. * Stocks with Implied Annualized Volatility(%) more than 100%. Above output shows the volat_remove_list, i.e. the stocks removed from the stockdata dataset due to its annualized volatility (